text: Emil Žnidar (born 27 February 1914, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics, representing Yugoslavia. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Yugoslavia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from the Municipality of Jesenice
